</p></li><li id="LI_929C0F12811B4096BB70DA320BD9C6C8" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Protective gloves: 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Microflex</b> 93-260. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-C02D66D1-E3CC-4BC2-95F8-775D93D93431" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-A97040BC-F110-4E4B-9CFF-E8082B9DA00E" class="- topic/note "><fig id="GUID-3B06D3E1-C4A2-42A3-9212-6DE96DA4938F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Avoid skin contact with ink: wear protective gloves. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7C716739-2AD7-42F8-8EF6-B28A8E7B1F76" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> Protect your eyes from splashing ink: wear safety glasses. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="GUID-410F43A8-6007-4C51-A178-C5B030AED80F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-1307D11F-0295-4F9F-A78D-93B250FFA47A-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-1307D11F-0295-4F9F-A78D-93B250FFA47A-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="SECTION_7BCF39D178844448B3A21E7E56376710" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to remove</title><table id="TABLE_5FBEFB7447DE4A1D819BDF873A72E3DB" pgwide="1" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove 1 screw and loosen the other screw of the locking bracket. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-851BC135-E91B-4606-9C8D-10EA3B50E655" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-EDD3BBDB-3DCC-4CCC-882F-0960BE5D048A-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-EDD3BBDB-3DCC-4CCC-882F-0960BE5D048A-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Remove the screw of the sensor bracket. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-09C200D2-D3BB-41CA-AD59-274BDF609CA1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-19F2841C-7726-41C8-8C0E-EAD8D9626F07-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-19F2841C-7726-41C8-8C0E-EAD8D9626F07-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Place the sensor bracket to the side. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-128004CD-87AE-4FAE-9995-EA0B0484B048" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-5F3A594D-2A8E-4EAC-AD79-98FCDF15D481-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-5F3A594D-2A8E-4EAC-AD79-98FCDF15D481-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Carefully pull out the ink leakage bin. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-D1F1A623-C871-4D4A-A957-BCDD448A914C" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-9B8F5658-8069-4D93-8B07-42B836AC1BF6-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-9B8F5658-8069-4D93-8B07-42B836AC1BF6-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-234D70A5-41EC-40E2-9E43-4217D346F540" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to install</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_E3FC7EE10DDC46BA880F87671551C890" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Install in reverse order. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Reconnect the Service jumper, exit SDS and press 'Restart' on the operator panel. 
